org.apache.giraph.edge

接口 ReuseObjectsOutEdges<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • 类型参数:
    I - Vertex id
    E - Edge value
    所有超级接口:
    Iterable<Edge<I,E>>, OutEdges<I,E>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    所有已知实现类:
    ByteArrayEdges, IntNullArrayEdges, LongDoubleArrayEdges, LongDoubleHashMapEdges, LongNullArrayEdges, LongNullHashSetEdges

    public interface ReuseObjectsOutEdges<I extends org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable,E extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends OutEdges<I,E>
    Empty interface to characterize OutEdges implementations that don't keep references to the Edge (or id and value) objects they are passed. The Giraph infrastructure can exploit this characteristic by reusing Edge objects.

    • 方法概要

      • 从接口继承的方法 java.lang.Iterable

        iterator

      • 从接口继承的方法 org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

        readFields, write
